snippet: Minnesota’s acting head coach, Tracy Claeys, said he did not expect Coach Jerry Kill to return from his leave of absence in time to be with the Gophers on Saturday at Northwestern.
abstract: Minnesota acting head coach Tracy Claeys says he does not expect coach Jerry Kill to return from leave of absence in time for game against Northwestern.
lead_paragraph: Minnesota’s acting head coach, Tracy Claeys, said he did not expect Coach Jerry Kill to return from his leave of absence in time to be with the Gophers on Saturday at Northwestern.
